---
description: Database & Prisma 7 rules
globs: ["prisma/**", "lib/db/**", "generated/**", "server/repositories/**", "prisma.config.ts"]
---
**Prisma 7 only** — see `.cursor/rules/000-stack-prisma7-supabase.mdc` and `docs/architecture/database.md`.

- Generator: `prisma-client` with output `generated/prisma/`.
- Import client from `@/generated/prisma/client`; use singleton `lib/db/prisma.ts`.
- Migrations via `prisma.config.ts` + `DIRECT_URL`; runtime via `@prisma/adapter-pg` + `DATABASE_URL`.
- Every business-owned entity has `organizationId`; queries filter by membership.
- Money in integer cents; timestamps UTC. Index common lookups.
- No Prisma in client components. No destructive migrations without explicit confirmation.
